%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pakistanis%20among%20six%20killed%20in%20shooting%20near%20mosque%20in%20Oman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721138061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F803c%2Flive%2F1f3125a0-431a-11ef-be3a-69a45cb4e7f8.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn38vx7g2e5o%231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20gunmen%20were%20also%20killed%20by%20security%20forces%20in%20what%20Pakistan%20condemned%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrorist%20attack%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A365%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn38vx7g2e5o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn38vx7g2e5o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcn38vx7g2e5o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Usha%20Chilukuri%20did%20first%20after%20Trump%20picked%20Vance%20as%20running%20mate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721136648000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111787352%2Cimgsize-1192565.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhat-usha-chilukuri-did-first-after-trump-picked-vance-as-running-mate%2Farticleshow%2F111787343.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%8BIn%20her%20statement%2C%20Usha%20Chilukuri%20said%20she%20would%20like%20to%20focus%20in%20caring%20for%20the%20family%20but%20speculations%20are%20rife%20that%20the%20decision%20was%20because%20Vance's%20political%20career%20as%20Donald%20Trump%20would%20not%20like%20a%20VP%20pick%20who%20is%20hugely%20talked%20about%20in%20mainstream%20media.%20Questions%20are%20also%20being%20raised%20as%20to%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20conflict%20of%20interest.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhat-usha-chilukuri-did-first-after-trump-picked-vance-as-running-mate%2Farticleshow%2F111787343.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Engineer%20Stole%20NEET%20Question%20Paper%20From%20Exam%20Body's%20Trunk%2C%20Arrested%20By%20CBI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20who%20stole%20NEET-UG%20paper%20from%20the%20trunk%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20in%20Bihar's%20Hazaribagh%20before%20they%20were%20allegedly%20leaked%20and%20his%20associate%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20today%2C%20sources%20said.%C2%A0Pankaj%20Kumar%2C%20who%20stole%20the%20paper%2C%20has%20been%20arrested%20from%20Patna%20while%20Raju%20Singh%20was%20caught%20in%20Jamshedpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20aka%20Aaditya%20did%20his%20civil%20engineering%20from%20NIT%20Jamshedpur%20in%202017%2C%20the%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cstrong%3ELeak%20Had%20Genesis%20In%20Hazaribagh%3A%20CBI%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20had%20earlier%20zeroed%20in%20on%20Hazaribagh%20as%20the%20origin%20place%20of%20the%20NEET-UG%20paper%20leak.%20The%20paper%20was%20leaked%20by%20Oasis%20school%20in%20Hazari%20Bagh%2C%20the%20CBI%20probe%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20two%20sets%20of%20papers%20which%20reached%20there%20had%20their%20seals%20broken%20and%20instead%20of%20flagging%20the%20issue%20the%20staff%20of%20the%20school%20remained%20tight-lipped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNine%20sets%20of%20question%20papers%20were%20dispatched%20from%20SBI%20Hazaribagh%20to%20different%20centres.%20The%20ones%20that%20reached%20Oasis%20school%20centre%20had%20their%20seals%20broken.%20The%20staff%20there%20did%20not%20raise%20an%20alarm%20and%20thus%2C%20their%20role%20is%20established%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20disclosed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBased%20on%20technical%20evidence%2C%20they%20had%20made%20searches%20in%20Learn%20and%20Play%20School%20in%20Patna%20where%20some%20burnt%20papers%20were%20recovered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained%20adding%20that%20the%20case%20was%20later%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Bihar%20Economic%20Offences%20Unit%20(EOU).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2021%2C%20the%20NTA%20disclosed%20that%20the%20code%20matched%20the%20papers%20found%20in%20Oasis%20school%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20principal%20of%20the%20school%2C%20Dr%20Ehsanul%20Haque%2C%20was%20also%20the%20district%20coordinator%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam%20in%20Hazaribagh%20and%20vice-principal%20Imtiaz%20Alam%20was%20the%20centre%20coordinator.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%2C%20which%20is%20probing%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20the%20medical%20entrance%20exam%2C%20has%20registered%20several%20First%20Information%20Reports%20(FIRs)%20and%20made%20nearly%2060%20arrests%20so%20far.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NEET-UG%20exam%20-%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20for%20admissions%20to%20MBBS%2C%20BDS%2C%20AYUSH%20and%20other%20related%20courses%20in%20government%20and%20private%20institutions%20-%20was%20held%20on%20May%205%20this%20year.%20The%20exam%20has%20been%20mired%20in%20controversy%2C%20with%20allegations%20of%20cheating%20and%20impersonation.%20The%20CBI%20FIR%20from%20Bihar%20pertains%20to%20paper%20leaks%2C%20while%20those%20registered%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Maharashtra%2C%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20impersonation%20of%20candidates%20and%20cheating.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20exam%20was%20conducted%20on%20May%205%20at%204%2C750%20centres%20in%20571%20cities%2C%20including%2014%20abroad.%20More%20than%2023%20lakh%20candidates%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E67%20Students%20Scored%20Perfect%20720%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESixty-seven%20students%20had%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20this%20year's%20exam%2C%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20NTA's%20history%2C%20with%20six%20from%20a%20Haryana%20centre%20figuring%20in%20the%20list%2C%20raising%20suspicion%20about%20irregularities%20in%20the%20examination.%20It%20was%20alleged%20that%20grace%20marks%20contributed%20to%20the%2067%20students%20sharing%20the%20top%20rank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20candidates%20sharing%20the%20top%20rank%20was%20reduced%20to%2061%20from%2067%20as%20the%20NTA%20announced%20the%20revised%20results%20on%20July%201%20after%20conducting%20a%20retest%20for%201%2C563%20candidates.%20Forty-eight%20per%20cent%20of%20students%20who%20were%20scheduled%20to%20retake%20the%20exam%20on%20June%2024%20did%20not%20turn%20up.%20Of%20the%20total%2C%20813%20(52%20per%20cent)%20gave%20the%20retest%20and%20750%20skipped%2C%20the%20data%20released%20by%20the%20NTA%20showed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20has%20also%20been%20riddled%20with%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leaks%20which%20are%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721136540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kin8q6g_entrance-exam-generic_625x300_14_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-more-arrested-by-cbi-6117975%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20who%20stole%20NEET-UG%20paper%20from%20the%20trunk%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20agency%20before%20they%20were%20allegedly%20leaked%20and%20his%20associate%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20CBI%20today%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-more-arrested-by-cbi-6117975%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-more-arrested-by-cbi-6117975%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-paper-leak-case-2-more-arrested-by-cbi-6117975%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'RCB%20was%20only%20about%20Kohli%2C%20de%20Villiers%2C%20Gayle'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721135537000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-111787044%2Cimgsize-78486.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Frcb-was-only-about-kohli-de-villiers-gayle-former-player-makes-startling-revelation%2Farticleshow%2F111786995.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(RCB)%20wicketkeeper%20Parthiv%20Patel%20made%20a%20startling%20revelation%20about%20the%20IPL%20franchise%2C%20highlighting%20the%20team%20culture%20which%20has%20always%20been%20about%20individuals%20rather%20than%20fostering%20a%20cohesive%20team%20environment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Frcb-was-only-about-kohli-de-villiers-gayle-former-player-makes-startling-revelation%2Farticleshow%2F111786995.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Haryana%2C%20Amit%20Shah's%20Anti-Congress%20Warning%20On%20Muslim%20Reservation%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20Tuesday%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bsnatched%20reservation%20from%20backward%20classes%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah's%C2%A0%20comment%20was%20made%20in%20Haryana%2C%20which%20will%20hold%20an%20Assembly%20election%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Congress%20forms%20the%20government%2C%20they%20will%20do%20the%20same%20in%20Haryana%20too...%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20a%20Backward%20Classes%20Samman%20Sammelan.He%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20always%20been%20against%20the%20backward%20classes%2C%20raking%20up%20a%20row%20-%20the%20issue%20of%20reservations%20to%20Muslims%20-%20that%20was%20big%20news%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20all-out%20and%20fierce%20attack%20on%20his%20rival%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20referred%20to%20the%201957%20Kaka%20Kalelkar%20Commission%20report%20and%20pointed%20out%20the%20Congress%20had%20delayed%20implementing%20its%20recommendations.%20%26quot%3BIn%201980%2C%20Indira%20Gandhi%20shelved%20the%20Mandal%20Commission.%20When%20it%20was%20introduced%20in%201990%2C%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20opposed%20OBC%20reservation...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20declared%20that%20it%20was%20only%20in%202014%2C%20after%20Narendra%20Modi%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20there%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bgovernment%20of%20Dalits%2C%20poor%2C%20and%20backward%20people%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20reference%20to%20the%20fact%2027%20of%2071%20cabinet%20ministers%20are%20from%20backward%20classes.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20assure%20you%20we%20will%20not%20allow%20Muslim%20reservation%20in%20Haryana%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20comment%20came%20in%20Haryana%20is%20seen%20as%20significant%2C%20since%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%2C%20who%20replaced%20ML%20Khattar%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election%2C%20is%20from%20the%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20last%20month%20Mr%20Saini%20said%20reservation%20for%20backward%20classes%20in%20Group-A%20and%20Group-B%20government%20jobs%2C%20currently%20at%2015%20per%20cent%2C%20would%20be%20increased%20to%2027%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20he%20said%2C%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bin%20line%20with%20the%20central%20government's%20policy%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20hit%20back%20strongly%2C%20directing%20Mr%20Shah%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20the%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20of%20Chief%20Minister%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20is%20in%20power.%20The%20TDP%20is%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%3B%20its%2016%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20are%20essential%20for%20Mr%20Modi%20to%20remain%20in%20power%20after%20the%20BJP's%20less%20than%20stellar%20poll%20result%2C%20in%20which%20it%20finished%2032%20seats%20of%20outright%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reference%20was%20to%20the%20TDP%20government's%20reservation%20policy%20for%20Muslims%2C%20who%20form%20a%20crucial%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Naidu%20has%20offered%20no%20indication%20he%20will%20scrap%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20his%20son%20Nara%20Lokesh%20told%20NDTV%20last%20month%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20(reservation%20for%20Muslims)%20has%20been%20going%20around%20for%20the%20last%20two%20decades.%20We%20stand%20by%20it.%20We%20intend%20to%20continue%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20fact%20minorities%20continue%20to%20suffer%20and%20that%20they%20have%20the%20lowest%20per%20capita%20income.%20As%20a%20government%2C%20it%20is%20our%20responsibility%20to%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20poverty.%20So%20whatever%20decisions%20I%20take%20are%20not%20for%20appeasement%2C%20but%20to%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20poverty.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20election%20campaign%20the%20Muslim%20reservation%20issue%20was%20a%20major%20bone%20of%20contention%2C%20particularly%20after%20Mr%20Modi's%20comment%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20plans%20in%20the%20Congress'%20manifesto%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Beconomic%20and%20institutional%20report%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20a%20national%20caste%20survey%2C%20and%20to%20a%20remark%20by%20his%20predecessor%2C%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20the%20PM%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20says%20they%20will%20calculate%20gold%20with%20mothers%20and%20sisters...%20and%20distribute%20that%20property....%20that%20Muslims%20have%20first%20right%20on%20all%20resources...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20provoked%20an%20angry%20response%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20accused%20Mr%20Modi%20of%20lying%20to%20divert%20voters'%20attention%20from%20genuine%20issues.%20The%20party%20pointed%20out%20its%20manifesto%20made%20no%20such%20claim%2C%20and%20Mr%20Gandhi%20explained%20the%20survey%20and%20its%20components%20were%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20step%26quot%3B%20in%20understanding%20how%20sections%20of%20the%20society%20developed%20and%20what%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20equality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20also%20complained%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission.%20A%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20BJP%20chief%20JP%20Nadda%20-%20and%20his%20Congress%20counterpart%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20against%20Mr%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Shah%20is%20on%20his%20second%20visit%20to%20poll-bound%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20was%20won%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20then%20ally%2C%20former%20ex-Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Dushyant%20Chautala's%20JJP%20in%20the%20last%20election.%20It%20was%20swept%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20two%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3B%20the%20party%20won%20all%2010%20seats.%20But%20in%20the%202024%20poll%20the%20Congress%20made%20a%20strong%20comeback%2C%20winning%20five%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721135400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F5g5uq8j8_amit-shah_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-shah-in-haryana-amit-shahs-anti-congress-warning-on-muslim-reservation-6118666%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20Tuesday%2C%20accusing%20the%20party%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bsnatched%20reservation%20from%20backward%20classes%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20giving%20it%20to%20Muslims%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fharyana-assembly-election-muslim-reservation-amit-sh