she%20said%2C%20her%20eyes%20welling%20up.%20She%20said%20the%20government%20must%20and%20will%20respond%20to%20these%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Thapa%20was%20a%20second%20generation%20Army%20officer%20and%20his%20father%20Colonel%20Bhuwanesh%20Thapa%20(retired)%20told%20ANI%20that%20he%20is%20proud%20that%20his%20son%20had%20sacrificed%20his%20life%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20could%20not%20believe%20when%20I%20was%20informed%20that%20he%20was%20no%20more.%20He%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20right%20from%20his%20childhood.%20He%20used%20to%20wear%20my%20Army%20dress%20and%20roam%20around.%20Even%20after%20he%20completed%20his%20engineering%2C%20he%20still%20wanted%20to%20join%20the%20Army.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20cleared%20the%20exam%20in%20the%20first%20attempt%20and%20joined%20the%20Army.%20I%20feel%20proud%20that%20my%20son%20has%20done%20something%20for%20the%20security%20of%20the%20nation.%20The%20sad%20part%20is%20we%20won't%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20him%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20veteran%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYogesh%20Thapa%2C%20the%20young%20officer's%20uncle%2C%20urged%20the%20Centre%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20the%20terrorists.%20%26quot%3BHe%20joined%20the%20service%20five%20years%20ago.%20He%20was%20unmarried.%20As%20a%20family%2C%20the%20loss%20we%20have%20suffered%20is%20impossible%20to%20cope%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20Captain%20Thapa%2C%20Naik%20D%20Rajesh%20and%20sepoys%20Bijendra%20and%20Ajay%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20encounter%20that%20began%20last%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20encounter%20broke%20out%20after%20a%20joint%20team%20of%20the%20Army%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20police%20launched%20a%20search%20in%20Doda%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20intelligence%20inputs.%20White%20Knight%20Corps%20said%20the%20gunfight%20between%20forces%20and%20terrorists%20began%20around%209%20pm%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5C