e-photos-35-1721126331-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Ffeature-photos-35-1721126331-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357111%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHe%20has%20travelled%20over%2060%2C000%20km%20on%20his%20bike%20so%20far.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20food%2C%20we%20avoid%20high-end%20restaurants%2C%20opting%20for%20local%20eateries%20instead.%20We%20also%20carry%20bread%20and%20peanut%20butter%20for%20breakfasts%20and%20sometimes%20cook%20in%20Airbnbs%20which%20helps%20save%20on%20food%20expenses.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20push%20yourself%2C%20enjoy%20the%20journey!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERiding%20for%20long%20hours%20can%20be%20taxing%20but%20according%20to%20Tejas%2C%20it%20becomes%20easy%20with%20every%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPhysically%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20follow%20a%20strict%20fitness%20routine%20but%20occasionally%20hit%20the%20gym.%20Our%20bodies%20have%20adapted%20to%20long%20rides%2C%20making%20biking%20more%20comfortable%20than%20long%20car%20journeys.%20The%20connection%20with%20our%20bike%20has%20developed%20over%20time%2C%20making%20long-distance%20rides%20manageable%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Three%20Magic%20Words%3A%C2%A0%20Plan%2C%20Plan%20%26amp%3B%20Plan!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20planning%20their%20first%20long-distance%20bike%20trip%2C%20thorough%20planning%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CStart%20with%20shorter%20distances%2C%20covering%20200-300%20km%20per%20day%2C%20and%20gradually%20increase%20as%20you%20become%20more%20comfortable.%20Consider%20the%20road%20conditions%20and%20weather%2C%20especially%20in%20hilly%20areas.%20Investing%20in%20a%20riding%20class%20can%20be%20beneficial%2C%20teaching%20you%20how%20to%20handle%20various%20terrains%20and%20unexpected%20situations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBook%20your%20accommodations%20ahead%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20book%20accommodations%20through%20platforms%20like%20MMT%2C%20Booking.com%2C%20and%20Airbnb%2C%20and%20sometimes%20collaborate%20with%20properties%20if%20they%20have%20approved%20for%20a%20partnership%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20What%20not%20to%20do%20on%20long%20travels%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommon%20mistakes%20new%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F314699%2Fbengaluru-startup-electric-motorcycle-bike-expedition-trip-across-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebike%20travellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20make%20include%20underestimating%20the%20importance%20of%20preparation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2w3Q6_MAA5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2w3Q6_MAA5%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%