just%20a%20few%20hours%20ago%2C%20the%20post%20has%20accumulated%20more%20than%20905%2C000%20views.%20Social%20media%20users%20reacted%20to%20the%20post%20with%20all%20kinds%20of%20reactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3Bit's%20impossible%20to%20beat%20the%20food.%20It's%20the%20tastiest%20cuisine%20of%20any%20human%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20user.%20%26quot%3BLmao%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20tweets%20ever%20about%20JD%20Vance.%20Hahahaha.%20Epic%2C%26quot%3B%20expressed%20another.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-jd-vances-wife-usha-vance-said-about-her-hindu-upbringing-its-influence-on-life-6116180%5C%22%3ETrump's%20Vice%20President%20Pick%20Reveals%20How%20His%20Hindu%20Wife%20Helped%20Him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fanand-mahindra-shares-picture-of-us-senator-jd-vances-indian-wedding-calls-it-6117042%5C%22%3EJD%20Vance%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20in%20the%20spotlight%20after%20former%20US%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20declared%20him%20his%20running%20mate.%20Vance's%20wife%2C%20Usha%2C%20a%20daughter%20of%20Indian%20immigrants%2C%20has%20established%20herself%20as%20a%20successful%20lawyer%2C%20having%20worked%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20US%2C%20the%20US%20Court%20of%20Appeals%20and%20a%20prestigious%20San%20Francisco%20firm%20until%20her%20recent%20exit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20San%20Diego%20suburb%20and%20attended%20Mt.%20Carmel%20High%20School.%20She%20graduated%20with%20a%20BA%20in%20history%20from%20Yale%20University%20in%202007.%20She%20later%20pursued%20further%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20earning%20an%20MPhil%20in%202009%20as%20a%20Gates%20Cambridge%20Scholar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJD%20Vance%20has%20often%20credited%20Usha%20for%20her%20support%20in%20his%20success.%20The%20c