old%20PTI%20on%20the%20phone%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20road%20to%20the%20spot%20where%20the%20temple%20has%20been%20built%20passes%20through%20difficult%20terrain%20and%20remains%20closed%20during%20monsoon%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20structure%20made%20of%20wood%20and%20stone%20is%20a%20small%20temple.%20It%20is%20illegal%20and%20built%20on%20no%20man's%20land%2C%26quot%3B%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20(SP)%20Akshay%20Prahlad%20Konde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20seems%20that%20some%20locals%20helped%20him%20build%20the%20structure%20after%20he%20told%20them%20that%20he%20had%20received%20divine%20orders%20to%20construct%20it%20in%20a%20dream.%20The%20self-styled%20godman%20has%20been%20living%20in%20the%20temple%20for%20the%20last%2010-12%20days%20and%20bathing%20in%20the%20sacred%20lake%2C%20Devi%20Kund%2C%20the%20SP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20caused%20resentment%20among%20the%20residents%20of%20the%20nearby%20villages%20who%20feel%20it%20is%20an%20act%20of%20desecration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20locals%20revere%20the%20lake%20and%20bathe%20their%20deities%20in%20it%20once%20in%20a%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20Konde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20self-styled%20godman%20managed%20to%20convince%20some%20locals%20to%20help%20him%2C%20many%20others%20refused%20to%20be%20taken%20in%20by%20his%20theory%20and%20approached%20the%20administration%20demanding%20action%20against%20him%2C%20the%20SP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20examining%20the%20matter%20from%20the%20law%20and%20order%20point%20of%20view%20but%20as%20the%20structure%20is%20located%20on%20no%20man's%20land%20in%20an%20eco-sensitive%20zone%2C%20the%20forest%20department%20will%20have%20to%20be%20involved%20for%20any%20action%20against%20the%20encroachment%2C%26quot%3B%20Konde%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20spot%20is%20hard%20to%20reach%20and%20it%20takes%20two-three%20days%20to%20reach%20it%