a%20had%20a%20candidate%20this%20tough%20was%20Theodore%20Roosevelt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20was%20on%20stage%20at%20a%20campaign%20rally%20on%20Saturday%20when%20gunshots%20rang%20out%20and%20Secret%20Service%20agents%20stormed%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20the%20shooting%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20bullet%20pierced%20the%20upper%20part%20of%20his%20right%20ear.%20In%20addition%2C%20one%20of%20the%20rally%20attendee%20was%20killed%20and%20two%20others%20were%20injured%20in%20the%20shooting%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Federal%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(FBI)%20identified%20the%20gunman%20as%20Thomas%20Matthew%20Crooks%2C%2020%2C%20from%20Bethel%20Park%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20with%20the%20case%20continuing%20to%20be%20under%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721119680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8trrs42_elon-musk_625x300_15_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-denies-pledging-45-million-a-month-for-trump-election-6116809%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tesla%20CEO%20Elon%20Musk%20has%20rejected%20a%20report%20claiming%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20give%20%2445%20million%20a%20month%20to%20a%20new%20super%20political-action%20committee%20(PAC)%20supporting%20former%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20presidential%20run%2C%20calling%20it%20%26quot%3Bfake.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-denies-pledging-45-million-a-month-for-trump-election-6116809%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-denies-pledging-45-million-a-month-for-trump-election-6116809%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Felon-musk-denies-pledging-45-million-a-month-for-trump-election-6116809%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump's%20Vice%20President%20Pick%20Reveals%20How%20His%20Hindu%20Wife%20Helped%20Him%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20Senator%20JD%20Vance%2C%20who%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20chose%20as%20his%20running%20mate%2C%20has%20credited%20his%20Hindu%20wife%20Usha%20Chilukuri%20Vance%20for%20shaping%20his%20personal%20and%20spiritual%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%2C%20he%20explained%20how%20his%20Indian-origin%20wife's%20Hindu%20faith%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20helping%20him%20navigate%20challenges%20and%20reconcile%20his%20Catholic%20beliefs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20revealed%20he%20%26quot%3Bwas%20raised%20Christian%20but%20never%20baptised.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20first%20baptised%20in%202018.%20Usha%20was%20actually%20raised%20non-Christian.%20But%20I%20remember%20when%20I%20started%20to%20re-engage%20with%20my%20faith%2C%20Usha%20was%20very%20supportive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%2038-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20met%20at%20Yale%20Law%20School%20and%20married%20in%20Kentucky%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20had%20two%20ceremonies%20-%20a%20traditional%20wedding%20ceremony%20and%20a%20separate%20Hindu%20ceremony%20conducted%20by%20a%20Hindu%20priest%2C%20honouring%20Usha's%20Hindu%20heritage.%20They%20have%20three%20children%20-%20Ewan%2C%206%2C%20Vivek%2C%204%2C%20and%20Mirabel%2C%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%2C%20reflecting%20on%20her%20upbringing%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Breligious%20household%26quot%3B%2C%20attributed%20her%20support%20for%20Vance's%20religious%20journey%20to%20her%20parents'%20influence.%20%26quot%3BMy%20parents%20are%20Hindu%20and%20that's%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20made%20them%20such%20good%20parents%20and%20good%20people.%20And%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20power%20of%20that%20in%20my%20own%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Usha.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20knew%20that%20JD%20was%20searching%20for%20something.%20This%20just%20felt%20right%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20parents'%20Hindu%20faith%20made%20them%20great%20parents%E2%80%9D%20-%20Usha%20Vance%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnShe's%20a%20Hindu%20%26amp%3B%20was%20supportive%20of%20her%20husband's%20rediscovery%20of%20his%20own%20faith%20(One%20of%20her%20sons%20is%20named%20Vivek%20too%20%3F%3F%3F%3F)%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnVance%2C%20anti-war%20%26amp%3B%20Trump's%20VP%2C%20so%20far%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20net%20positive%20for%20India%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKtbOUNT9ba%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKtbOUNT9ba%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Alexei%20Arora%20(%40AlexeiArora)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAlexeiArora%2Fstatus%2F1812939370523160971%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2015%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20they%20raise%20their%20children%2C%20given%20their%20different%20religious%20backgrounds%2C%20Usha%20stressed%20the%20importance%20of%20communication.%20%26quot%3BWe%20just%20talk%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20stating%20there%20are%20certain%20values%20and%20principles%20that%20she%20and%20Vance%20%26quot%3Bsimply%20agree%20on%26quot%3B%20family%20matters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUsha%20Chilukuri%20Vance%20is%20a%20lawyer%2C%20as%20per%20her%20LinkedIn%20profile.%20She%20was%20raised%20in%20a%20San%20Diego%20suburb%20and%20attended%20Mt.%20Carmel%20High%20School.%20She%20graduated%20with%20a%20BA%20in%20history%20from%20Yale%20University%20in%202007.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20later%20pursued%20further%20studies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Cambridge%2C%20earning%20an%20MPhil%20in%202009%20as%20a%20Gates%20Cambridge%20Scholar.%20She%20worked%20as%20an%20associate%20at%20Munger%2C%20Tolles%20%26amp%3B%20Olson%20LLP.%20She%20was%20a%20Law%20Clerk%20at%20the%20Supreme%