o%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20has%20over%20900%20farmers%2C%20while%20the%20entire%20taluka%20has%202%2C000%20farmers.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20initially%20formed%20to%20bring%20small%20farmers%20together%20and%20help%20them%20take%20their%20produce%20to%20the%20market%20directly%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Omkar%20Sapre%2C%20the%20board%20member%20and%20advisor%20of%20the%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201068px)%20100vw%2C%201068px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221068%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Devgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20Limited%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20protect%20their%20mangoes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350.jpeg%201068w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-300x200.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-500x333.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-768x512.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdevgad4-1720776350-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356710%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22712%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDevgad%20Taluka%20Mango%20Grower%E2%80%99s%20Co-operative%20Society%20Limited%20have%20found%20a%20unique%20way%20to%20protect%20their%20mangoes%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20selling%20online%2C%20especially%20post%20COVID-19%2C%20which%20allowed%20us%20to%20reach%20customers%20directly.%20When%20you%20visit%20markets%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20you%20see%20many%20people%20selling%20the%20Devgad%20variety.%20Either%20they