%20the%20couple%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20and%20they%20believe%20they%20would%20get%20the%20return%20on%20investment%20within%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20limitations%20of%20the%20entire%20grid-backed%20setup%2C%20Shilpa%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20we%20developed%20a%20habit%20of%20running%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20the%20mixer%2C%20water%20pumps%20only%20in%20the%20solar%20hours%20between%2010am%20to%205pm%20or%20it%20will%20lead%20to%20storage%20exhaustion.%20We%20run%20four%20ACs%20in%20the%20day%20and%20only%20two%20at%20night.%20You%20require%20this%20kind%20of%20discipline.%20But%20these%20are%20all%20matters%20of%20choice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fsolar-2-1720701386-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356504%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20harness%20solar%20energy%20to%20use%20energy%20consuming%20appliances%20like%20induction%2C%20microwave%2C%20washing%20machine.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2F