0that%20for%20civil%20services%2C%20requiring%20candidates%20to%20put%20in%20more%20effort%20right%20from%20the%20preliminary%20stage.%20I%20had%20to%20elevate%20my%20Prelims%20preparation%20to%20a%20whole%20new%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Harsimran%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-2-1720617509-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356341%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHarsimran%20secured%20210%20marks%20out%20of%20300%20in%20the%20personality%20test%20round.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20prepare%20effectively%2C%20I%20searched%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F282477%2Fupsc-cse-syllabus-previous-years-question-paper-tips-ias-officer-anisha-shrivastav%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%20question%20papers%20%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20This%20helped%20me%20understand%20UPSC%E2%80%99s%20expectations%20and%20gauge%20the%20adequacy%20of%20my%20preparation.%20Additionally%2C%20