20I%20focused%20on%20technical%20aspects%20related%20to%20forestry%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20adding%20that%20during%20the%20interview%20round%2C%20he%20was%20asked%20about%20various%20types%20of%20forest%20fires%20and%20strategies%20to%20improve%20groundwater%20quality%20affected%20by%20the%20overuse%20of%20chemical%20fertilisers%20in%20farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Harsimran%20Singh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720620910000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FHarsimran-1-1720617346.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D356313%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Despite%20initial%20setbacks%20in%20UPSC%20CSE%20attempts%2C%20Harsimran%20Singh%20Cheema%20persisted%2C%20achieving%20an%20All%20India%20Rank%20of%2016%20in%20his%20first%20attempt%20at%20UPSC%20IFS%20in%202022.%20He%20shares%20the%20difference%20in%20preparation%20strategy%20for%20IAS%20and%20IFS%2C%20sharing%20tips%20that%20worked%20for%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356313%2Fupsc-cse-ifs-officer-harsimran-singh-cheema-preparation-tips-strategy-forest-services%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Exclusive%3A%20Krish%20Ashok%20On%20Debunking%20Food%20Myths%20%26amp%3B%20Misinformation%20in%20His%20%E2%80%98Masala%20Lab%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20mother%20used%20to%20travel%2C%20she%20would%20jot%20down%20simple%20recipes%20like%20%3Cem%3Esambhar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Erasam%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20basic%20%3Cem%3Esabzis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Eraitas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20curries.%20Despite%20our%20earnest%20efforts%20to%20replicate%20them%20exactly%20as%20written%2C%20my%20father%20and%20I%20could%20never%20quite%20match%20the%20taste%20of%20%3Cem%3Eamma%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn