%20in%20various%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LED%20light%20itself%20isn%E2%80%99t%20inherently%20threatening.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20the%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20perceived%20by%20the%20animals%20that%20makes%20it%20effective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20product%20that%20the%20company%20offers%20is%20the%20bioplastic%20scare%20system%2C%20which%20they%20call%20Kaapikat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20products%20provided%20by%20the%20startup%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356166%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20products%20provided%20by%20the%20startup%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20uses%20sensors%20to%20detect%20motion%20and%20plays%20different%20animal%20sounds%20to%20keep%20them%20away%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20monkeys.%20However%2C%20monkeys%20are%20very%20smart%20and%20their%20behaviour%20varies%20by%20region%2C%20so%20we%20only%20sell%20this%20product%20selectively%20and%20encourage%20farmers%20to%20test%20it%20in%20their%20area%20before%20making%20a%20larger%20purchase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20offer%20customised%20solutions%20combining%20light%20and%20sound%20deterrents%20for%20specific%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20flexibility%20allows%20us%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20types%20of%20wildlife%20and%20their%20unique%20behaviours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%982000%2B%20farmers%20benefitted%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20they%20faced%20initially%2C%20Ayan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20team%20consists%20of%204%20to%205%20dedicated%20members%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%20about%20two-and-a-half%20years%20to%20develop%20these%20products.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnderstanding%20the%20behaviour%20of%20different%20animals%20and%20how%20it%20changes%20with%20the%20seasons%20was%20crucial.%20For%20instance%2C%20elephants%20and%20wild%20boars%20behave%20differently%20in%20the%20winter%20compared%20to%20the%20summer.%20We%20conduct%20pilots%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%202%20to%203%20months%20to%20ensure%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20products%20over%20different%20seasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20challenges%20that%20he%20faced%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20information%20among%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farmers%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20understand%20how%20a%20simple%20light%20could%20deter%20animals%20when%20they%20were%20experiencing%20significant%20problems%20with%20wildlife.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20conducted%20numerous%20demonstrations%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20and%20farmer-produce%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyan%20ran%20pilots%20for%203-6